AND A LOCATION.

00:36.245 --> 00:38.706
YOU'VE GOT BOTH.
- I WANT TO ENLIST.

00:38.706 --> 00:41.167
- PHILLIP.
- IT'S LIP.

00:41.167 --> 00:44.378
- IT'S JUST GALLAGHER NOW.
GET ON.

00:44.378 --> 00:47.381
- I WANT YOU TO BREAK MY LEG.
I NEED THE INSURANCE MONEY.

00:47.381 --> 00:49.383
IT'S THE ONLY WAY I'LL BE ABLE
TO PAY FOR THE TRANSPLANT.

00:49.383 --> 00:51.093
[bone snaps]
AAH!

00:51.093 --> 00:53.179
MY OWN DAUGHTER ISN'T EVEN
A MATCH!

00:53.179 --> 00:55.389
- DAUGHTER?
- OH, FUCK IT.

00:55.389 --> 01:00.145
- [screaming]
GET...OUT!

01:00.145 --> 01:01.729
- YOU KNOW, I'M GETTING PRETTY
DAMN TIRED OF EVERYBODY

01:01.729 --> 01:04.232
TELLING ME WHERE I SHOULD BE
AND WHAT I SHOULD BE DOING.

01:04.232 --> 01:05.691
- WELL, THEN, STOP MAKING THEM
HAVE TO!

01:05.691 --> 01:07.109
GROW THE FUCK UP!

01:07.109 --> 01:09.737
- I NEED A-A BEER
FOR MY DAUGHTER HERE.

