02:14.009 --> 02:17.221
♪ WHAT IS THIS DOWNSIDE ♪

02:17.221 --> 02:21.184
♪ THAT YOU SPEAK OF? ♪

02:21.184 --> 02:23.143
♪ WHAT IS THIS FEELING ♪

02:23.143 --> 02:26.230
♪ YOU'RE SO SURE OF? ♪

